latestPosts.caption:
Theyyam x Chsaddler | Where Tradition Meets Adrenaline 🔥
Countless hours. Limitless passion.
This isn’t just a bike stunt video ,it’s a soul-stirring tribute to one of the most powerful art forms of our land.
From ancient rituals to roaring off-road chaos, this is a fusion of fire and fury.

The bike? Hand-painted with the spirit of Theyyam , not just design, but living art.
Every stroke on that tank tells a story. Hats off to the brilliant team ( @wabisabistudio__ ) who poured their heart into creating this masterpiece.

What you’re about to witness is devotion on wheels.
A journey where culture rides shotgun and chaos holds the throttle.
Every dust-kissed drift, every roar of the engine, every frame — a celebration of heritage, craftsmanship, and adrenaline.

Huge shoutout to the visionary editor who stitched this story with soul ( @shutter.engineer ), and to the one who captured the raw essence of Theyyam through the lens ( @thrilokam )— your work gave life to this project in the most powerful way.

We didn’t just make a video.
We summoned a legend.
Welcome to the madness.

#TheyyamXChsaddler #RideOfTheGods #HandPaintedBeast #theyyam #artwork
